Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.50,0:22:24.90,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5} A nossa compatibilidade
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.90,0:22:28.23,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}se um vidente dissesse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.23,0:22:31.49,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}que não é lá essas coisas
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:35.03,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}ele seria um impostor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.03,0:22:38.55,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Não, não pode, não se deixe enganar.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:42.49,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Quem decide o destino sou eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.49,0:22:44.34,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Isso mesmo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:49.31,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}este é o amor verdadeiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:55.15,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}É o tipo de coisa que, após morrermos
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.15,0:22:59.53,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}será exibida em um museu de arte.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.44,0:23:05.99,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Por isso, me deixe sempre em primeiro lugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:09.58,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Me ame com todo carinho
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.58,0:23:15.69,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}até que estas mãos que seguramos se fundam.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.69,0:23:19.59,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Vamos ficar sempre nessa vibe boa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:23.01,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Se formos nós dois, será moleza.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:29.22,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Fique ao meu lado, mesmo que estejamos "chapados" de amor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.22,0:23:32.07,Lyrics - IFM - ED,,0,0,0,karaoke,{\be6\fad(200,100)\blur5}Por favor.
